  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Profitability metrics indicate stable net margin performance, with Q3 2025 net margin at 27.86%, compared to 27.95% in Q2 2025, 26.84% in Q1 2025, and 25.80% in Q3 2024. This represents meaningful year-over-year margin expansion of approximately 206 basis points. However, gross profit and operating income data are not available in the provided financial statements, limiting visibility into the full profitability cascade. Net income for Q3 2025 totaled $2,902,000,000, reflecting continued earnings strength.",
